{"tid":184442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"問一套廿年前既港產劇(求神龍)","createTime":"2017-04-02T21:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T20:18:08.000Z","uid":60037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de7df9705f011dd581b3705207db6896b00751d7","tid":184442,"uid":60037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T21:18:00.000Z","msg":"果陣時我係好細個，<br />\n淨係記得套劇入便有個細路哥，<br />\n佢好似家庭唔正常又唔知點解，<br />\n總之佢係同一個好似佢阿哥或者佢阿叔既人係咪都係一齊，<br />\n喺果個細路哥失志既時候，果個阿哥就會安慰佢，<br />\n又成日一齊踢波，<br />\n後來果個阿哥好似因為工作點係唔知咩關係走去黑龍江，<br />\n(呢個係我記得最有可能問到既線索，走去黑龍江)，<br />\n跟住之後既劇情好似我就冇睇到，<br />\n唔知問唔問的到呢&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6473113bb6ed74f27bc28cfa03cf65718a7db65","tid":184442,"uid":60037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1622a4977d24898b1120842f4b28c507914105f","tid":184442,"uid":60037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"好想知果套劇係咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b73ef9a1d0b65ad8fa4833c4d090b6f2b646f5a6","tid":184442,"uid":2515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"有乜人做都唔知點幫你"},{"pid":"b7751ac599b2b42317552eba5cb825e45171c257","tid":184442,"uid":60037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T20:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有乜人做都唔知點幫你</blockquote><br />\nsorry&hellip;真係唔記得有咩人做，淨係記得主角係男童&hellip;"}]}